Temporary traffic signs will be in place to direct motorists to access either end of Cross Way Road via N.C. Highway 12 or Buxton Back Road.  Work is set to begin on the pipe replacement Monday at 8 a.m. and is scheduled to end by the end of the day Wednesday.(NCDOT)
